374
00:26:20.409 --> 00:26:23.036
which I have heard is spectacular.

375
00:26:23.162 --> 00:26:25.288
Who told you this?
Women you paid?

376
00:26:25.414 --> 00:26:26.998
And three. . .

377
00:26:27.917 --> 00:26:31.169
more gold than you can spend
if you Iived a thousand years.

378
