- No.
- You look like you're in agony.

473
00:35:00.429 --> 00:35:03.013
The fire is burning your pretty soft skin.

474
00:35:06.685 --> 00:35:08.269
- Ah!
- (Laughter)

475
00:35:10.021 --> 00:35:12.565
Damn you. woman.
